---
---
<section class="capabilities">
  <div class="container cap-container">
    <div class="cap-header">
      <h2 class="cap-title">
        We build high-converting ecommerce stores that don’t just look premium — they drive real sales.
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cap-content">
      <div class="cap-left">
        <div class="cap-image">
          <img src="/images/capabilities.png" alt="Ecommerce Capabilities" class="cap-main-img" />
          <div class="cap-tag">• Creative as it Should be</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="cap-right">
        <div class="capability-item active">
          <div class="cap-info">
            <h3>CONVERSION-FOCUSED DEVELOPMENT</h3>
            <div class="cap-desc">
              <p>From product pages to checkout optimization, every element is built to increase sales and maximize average order value.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cap-arrow">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="divider"></div>
        
        <div class="capability-item">
          <div class="cap-info">
            <h3>MULTI-PLATFORM EXPERTISE</h3>
            <div class="cap-desc">
              <p>We specialize in Shopify, WooCommerce, and custom headless solutions, ensuring your brand thrives across all digital touchpoints.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cap-arrow">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="capability-item">
          <div class="cap-info">
            <h3>SPEED OPTIMIZATION</h3>
            <div class="cap-desc">
              <p>Lightning-fast load times across all devices to reduce bounce rates and ensure a seamless shopping experience for your customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cap-arrow">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="capability-item">
          <div class="cap-info">
            <h3>DATA-DRIVEN SCALING</h3>
            <div class="cap-desc">
              <p>Utilizing advanced analytics and user behavior data to continuously iterate and scale your business to new heights.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cap-arrow">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const items = document.querySelectorAll('.capability-item');
  
  items.forEach(item => {
    item.addEventListener('click', () => {
      // Remove active from others
      items.forEach(i => i.classList.remove('active'));
      // Add to clicked
      item.classList.add('active');
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .capabilities {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 80px 0;
  }
  
  .cap-title {
    font-size: 44px; /* Reduced from 50.5px */
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
  
  .cap-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 80px;
  }
  
  .cap-left {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }
  
  .cap-main-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain; /* Changed to contain to show the whole artistic image */
  }
  
  .cap-tag {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .cap-right {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .capability-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 24px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-left: -24px; /* Align content by offsetting padding */
  }
  
  .capability-item.active {
    background-color: #EFECFF;
  }
  
  .cap-info h3 {
    font-size: 28.8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.8px;
    margin-bottom: 0px;
    transition: margin 0.3s ease;
  }

  .capability-item.active .cap-info h3 {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  
  .cap-desc {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 0fr;
    transition: grid-template-rows 0.3s ease;
  }

  .capability-item.active .cap-desc {
    grid-template-rows: 1fr;
  }

  .cap-desc p {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16.25px;
    opacity: 0.6;
    max-width: 460px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  
  .cap-arrow {
    width: 43px;
    height: 43px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  
  .capability-item.active .cap-arrow {
    background-color: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background-color: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.16);
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cap-content {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .cap-title {
      font-size: 36px;
    }
  }
</style>
